---
source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Select an option in a <select> element

Usage: bl select [OPTIONS] <selector> <value>

Arguments:
  <selector>  CSS selector or @ref of the <select> element
  <value>     Value of the option to select

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl select "select#color" "blue"
  # Select "blue" in the color dropdown
